          "reviewBody": "Writing this review gives me an immense  sense of pride and happiness, I've personally witnessed the journey Pearl Drop School has made in the past decade. It's a beacon of educational excellence.\n\nThe institution not only focuses on academic excellence but also wholistic development of children to be well rounded citizens of this modern era. Along with STEM focus, children have the opportunity to participate in various different athletic and cultural events.\n\nI appreciate the leadership team, teachers and administrative staff that take a lot of care and effort to run this amazing school.\n\nKudos to the Pearl Drop Team!",
